tr.th: Conclusion and Recommendations based on this report and previous findings known to us

tr.td: All parameters are within normal limits except for a mildly elevated HbA1c (6.1%), indicating impaired glucose metabolism or possible prediabetes. Renal function and electrolytes are normal. Recommend clinical correlation for diabetes risk and consideration of lifestyle modification or further evaluation as appropriate.
